&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in Excel/Google Sheets; experience with FP&amp;amp;A tools (e.g., Anaplan) and BI tools (e.g., Tableau, Power BI) is a plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have a proven track record of turning complex, multi-source financial data into reliable, well-structured reporting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactive and well-organized, with the ability to manage multiple workstreams effectively&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfortable working across functions and levels, including with senior stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
