&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Freenow is an equal opportunity employer and we consider qualified applicants regardless of race, religion, national origin, gender, gender identity, sexual orientation, disability or age. &lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;We want you to grow and evolve, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;bri

