&lt;p&gt;At Freenow, we are on a mission to empower smarter mobility decisions, helping people to move freely and cities to thrive.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;We believe our success starts with our people, culture, and leadership. As we continue to grow and evolve our European business, we are looking for an exceptional People Leader to help shape the future of our organization. The People Leader for Europe will report to Lyft&#39;s Chief People Officer, with a dotted-line relationship to the European leader and the Senior Director, People Business Partner at Lyft.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a senior People leader in Europe, this role serves as a trusted advisor to the European Leadership Team and a key member of both the Europe Leadership Team and Lyft&#39;s global People organization.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The role is responsible for translating global people strategy into regional impact while driving organizational effectiveness, talent strategy, culture, leadership, and transformation across Europe.&lt;/p&gt;
