&lt;li&gt;Coach senior leaders to improve leadership effectiveness and organizational performance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Shape a high-performance, inclusive, and accountable culture across Europe.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
