&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;People Leadership, AI &amp;amp; Scaling&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide dotted-line regional leadership across all European People functions, driving alignment and consistency without direct reporting authority.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead a high-impact People Business Partnering team across Europe.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive adoption of AI, analytics, and technology to improve decision-making, workforce insights, and efficiency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Scale People processes through automation and data-driven operating models.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
