&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Background&lt;/strong&gt; in data analysis and using metrics to drive operational decisions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Fluent in English&amp;nbsp; + &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Additional European languages&lt;/strong&gt; (German, French, Portuguese, Italian, Spanish) are a plus but not mandat

