&lt;p&gt;As a dynamic and charismatic leader, you will be the driving force behind our German operations. This isn&#39;t a role for a traditional manager; it’s for a strategic operator who can inspire a local growth team, negotiate with global functions, and execute with precision to propel Freenow’s market leadership.&lt;/p&gt;
