&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a talented and motivated&lt;strong&gt; Junior Social Media Manager &lt;/strong&gt;to join our team!&lt;br&gt;It&#39;s a &lt;strong&gt;6 months fixed term contract&lt;/strong&gt; opportunity.&lt;/p&gt;
