&lt;li&gt;Prepare creative briefs and ensure creators receive clear, timely feedback throughout the production process.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage contracts, documentation and administrative processes related to creator partnerships.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain social media content calendars across multiple markets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate with Product and Local Marketing teams across seven countries to align content with launches, campaigns and business priorities.&lt;/li&gt;
